"Disable Spaceship Particles","If you have FPS problems, setting this to true will help if spaceship particles are in your sights","Disable Spaceship Explosion","Spaceships will not explode on contact if set to true","Minimap Left","If true, this will move the Oxygen Indicator to the left side. You can combine this with \"Minimap Bottom\"","Minimap Bottom","If true, this will move the Oxygen Indicator to the bottom. You can combine this with \"Minimap Left\"","Disable Oxygen Collector Leaf Decay","If set to true, Oxygen Collectors will not consume leaf blocks.",
"Space Stations Require Permission","While true, space stations require you to invite other players using /ssinvite <playername>","Disable Space Station creation","If set to true on a server, players will be completely unable to create space stations.","Override Capes","By default, Galacticraft will override capes with the mod\'s donor cape. Set to false to disable.","Space Station Solar Energy Multiplier","If Mekanism is installed, solar panels will work (default 2x) more effective on space stations.","External Sealable IDs",
"List IDs of non-opaque blocks from other mods (for example, special types of glass) that the Oxygen Sealer should recognize as solid seals. Format is ID:METADATA","External Detectable IDs","List IDs from other mods that the Sensor Glasses should recognize as solid blocks. Format is ID:METADATA","Dungeon Boss Health Modifier","Change this is you wish to balance the mod (if you have more powerful weapon mods)","Suffocation Cooldown","Lower/Raise this value to change time between suffocation damage ticks","Suffocation Damage",
"Change this value to modify the damage taken per suffocation tick","Oil gen in external dimensions","List of non-galacticraft dimension IDs to generate oil in","Force Overworld Spawn","By default, you will respawn on galacticraft dimensions if you die. If you set this to true, you will respawn back on earth.","Enable Debug Messages","If this is enabled, debug messages will appear in the console. This is useful for finding bugs in the mod.","Enable Sealer Multithreading","(Experimental) If this is enabled, Oxygen Sealers seal checks will run in a separate thread - faster but there may be some artifacts.",
"Enable Sealed edge checks","If this is enabled, areas sealed by Oxygen Sealers will run a seal check when the player breaks or places a block (or on block updates).  This should be enabled for a 100% accurate sealed status is accurate, but can be disabled on servers for performance reasons.","Enable Copper Ore Gen","If this is enabled, copper ore will generate on the overworld.","Enable Tin Ore Gen","If this is enabled, tin ore will generate on the overworld.","Enable Aluminum Ore Gen","If this is enabled, aluminum ore will generate on the overworld.",
