"Conveyor.CaptureNonItems","If false, conveyors will not grab non-item entities. Breaks conveyor mob grinders but makes them safe for golems, etc.","Conveyor.NeverCapturePlayers","If true, conveyors will NEVER capture players regardless of other settings.","Conveyor.NeverCaptureTCGolems","If true, conveyors will NEVER capture Thaumcraft golems regardless of other settings.","PlaySounds","Set to false to disable the harvester\'s sound when a block is harvested.","Road.Slippery","SearchDistance.FruitTreeMaxHoriztonal",
