"LaserDrill.Cost","The work required by the drill to generate a single ore.","Meat.IncreasedSaturation","If true, meat will be worth steak saturation instead of cookie saturation.","FishDropRate","The rate at which fish are dropped from the fishing rod. The drop rate is 1 / this number. Must be greater than 0.","VanillaOverride.GlassPanes","If true, allows vanilla glass panes to connect to MFR stained glass panes.","VanillaOverride.Ice","If true, enables MFR unmelting ice as well as vanilla ice.","VanillaOverride.MilkBucket",
"If true, replaces the vanilla milk bucket so milk can be placed in the world.","RedNet.Debug","If true, RedNet cables will dump a massive amount of data to the log file. You should probably only use this if PC tells you to.","WorldGen.RubberTreeBiomeWhitelist","A comma-separated list of biomes to allow rubber trees to spawn in. Does nothing if rubber tree worldgen is disabled.","WorldGen.RubberTreeBiomeBlacklist","A comma-separated list of biomes to disallow rubber trees to spawn in. Overrides any other biomes added.",
"RedNet.ConnectionBlackList","A comma-separated list of block IDs to prevent RedNet cables from connecting to.","WorldGen.DimensionBlacklist","A comma-separated list of dimension IDs to disable MFR worldgen in. By default, MFR will not attempt worldgen in dimensions where the player cannot respawn.","WorldGen.LakeRarity.Sludge","Higher numbers make sludge lakes rarer. A value of one will be approximately one per chunk.","WorldGen.LakeRarity.Sewage","Higher numbers make sewage lakes rarer. A value of one will be approximately one per chunk.",
"Unifier.Blacklist","dyeBlue,dyeWhite,dyeBrown,dyeBlack,listAllwater,listAllmilk","A comma-separated list of ore dictionary entrys to disable unifying for. By default, MFR will not attempt to unify anything with more than one oredict name.","AutoSpawner.Blacklist","A comma-separated list of entity IDs (e.g.: CaveSpider,VillagerGolem,butterflyGE) to blacklist from the AutoSpawner.","RecipeSets","EnableVanillaRecipes","If true, MFR will register its standard (vanilla-item-only) recipes.","EnableThermalExpansionRecipes",
"If true, MFR will register its Thermal Expansion-based recipes.","EnableGregTechRecipes","If true, MFR will register its GregTech-based recipes.","Recipe.CheaperDSU","DSU.EnableCheaperRecipe","If true, the DSU can be built out of chests instead of ender pearls. Does nothing if the recipe is disabled.","Recipe.SingleDSU","DSU.CraftSingle","DSU recipes will always craft one DSU. Does nothing for recipes that already only craft one DSU (cheap mode, GT recipes, etc).","Recipe.MossyCobble","EnableMossyCobbleRecipe",
"If true, mossy cobble can be crafted.","Recipe.PortaSpawner","If true, the PortaSpawner will be craftable.","Recipe.Syringes","If true, the Syringes will be craftable.","Recipe.Guns","If true, the Guns will be craftable.","Recipe.NetLauncher","If true, the safarinet launcher will be craftable.","LiquidSyringes","If true, Empty Syringes will be able to contain liquids and inject players.","SPAMR.Exploding","If true, SPAMRs will explode when they run out of fuel.","Biofuel.Exploding","If true, biofuel will explode when in the nether.",
"WorldGen.SacredRubberSapling","If true, enable adding Sacred Rubber Sapling to jungle temple loot.","Machine",".IgnoreChunkLimit","If true, the Chunk Loader will ignore forgeChunkLoading.cfg.",".RequiresOwnerOnline","If true, the Chunk Loader will require that the player who placed it be online to function","Recipe.SmoothSlab","If true, smooth double stone slabs can be craftable.","Recipe.CheaperChunkLoader","If true, the ChunkLoader can be built out of cheaper materials. Does nothing if the recipe is disabled.",
