"The Force Engine will never explode or die of loneliness.","The Force Engine requires a redstone signal to run.","You can right-click the Force Engine with a valid liquid container to add liquid quickly.","Lava is also a valid Force Engine Fuel, although not as effective as Liquid Force.","Force Grinder","Force Crusher","Force Extractor","The Force Panel generates EU by collecting solar or lunar energy, although solar energy is more potent.","Placing Liquid Force next to the Force Panel at the same height will throttle the panel to gather more energy.",
