"openblocks.gui.laststand.content","openblocks.gui.flimflam.title","openblocks.gui.flimflam.content","§bActivate Reactor","§bDeactivate Reactor","Residual heat will still","generate power/consume coolant,","until the reactor cools.","§bAuto-Eject Waste","Waste in the core will be ejected","as soon as possible","§bDo Not Auto-Eject Waste","§dWaste must be manually ejected.","Ejection can be done from this","screen, or via rednet,","redstone or computer port signals.","§bEject Waste Now","Ejects waste from the core",
"into access ports.","Each 1000mB waste = 1 ingot","SHIFT: Dump excess waste, if any","Reactor Control","§bCore Temperature","Temperature inside the reactor core.","Higher temperatures increase fuel burnup.","§bFuel Burnup Rate","The rate at which fuel is","fissioned into waste in the core.","§bFuel Reactivity","How heavily irradiated the core is.","Higher levels of radiation","reduce fuel burnup.","§bCore Heat","Heat of the reactor\'s fuel.","High heat raises fuel usage.","Core heat is transferred to","the casing. Transfer rate",
"is based on the design of","the reactor\'s interior.","§bCasing Heat","Heat of the reactor\'s casing.","High heat raises energy output","and coolant conversion.","§bCoolant Fluid Tank","Casing heat will superheat","coolant in this tank.","§bHot Fluid Tank","Superheated coolant","will pump into this tank,","and must be piped out","via coolant ports","bigreactors:textures/gui/ReactorController.png","Status: §4Offline","Status: §2Online","%.0f millibuckets per tick","%.2f flux per tick"," C","  %.0f C","%2.0f%%",
"0 millibuckets per tick","%.","f millibuckets per tick","§bEnergy Output","This reactor is passively cooled","and generates energy directly from","the heat of its core.","§bHot Fluid Output","This reactor is actively cooled","by a fluid, such as water, which","is superheated by the core.","§bEject Fuel","Ejects fuel contained in the","reactor, placing ingots in the","reactor\'s access ports.","SHIFT: Dump excess fuel.","§bEject Waste","Ejects waste contained in the","SHIFT: Dump excess waste.","§bInlet Mode",
"Sets the access port to","inlet mode.","Port WILL accept","items from pipes/ducts.","Port WILL NOT eject","items to pipes/ducts.","§bOutlet Mode","outlet mode.","Port WILL NOT accept","Port WILL eject","ingots to pipes/ducts.","bigreactors:textures/gui/ReactorAccessPort.png","bigreactors:textures/gui/RedNetPort.png","Reactor RedNet Port","Settings","Commit","Control Rod: ","Activates On:","-- ALL --","INVALID: ","Pulse","Input: Toggle reactor on/off","Input: Change control rod insertion","Input: Eject Waste",
"Output: Fuel Temp (C)","Output: Casing Temp (C)","Output: Fuel mix (% fuel, 0-100)","Output: Fuel amount","Output: Waste amount","Output: Energy amount (%)","bigreactors:textures/gui/RedstonePort.png","Reactor Redstone Port","Pick a setting","Activate on Pulse","While On","While Off","Reset","Input - Eject Waste","Input - Control Rod Insertion","Output - Fuel Amount","Output - Waste Amount","Output - Fuel Enrichment %","Output - Fuel Temp (C)","Output - Casing Temp (C)","Output - Energy Amount (%)","Input - Enable/Disable",
"Set from Signal","Toggle on Pulse","Eject on Pulse","Set on Pulse","Insert on Pulse","Retract on Pulse","Active While Below","Active While Above","Set to","Insert by","Retract by","Milli-buckets","% of total contents, 0% if empty","Degrees centigrade","% of energy buffer filled, 0% if empty","bigreactors:textures/gui/TurbineController.png","Turbine Control","§bRotor Speed","Speed of the rotor in","revolutions per minute.","Rotors perform best at 900","or 1800 RPM.","Speeds over 2000PM are overspeed","and may cause a turbine to",
"fail catastrophically.","Turbines generate energy via","metal induction coils placed","around a spinning rotor.","More, or higher-quality, coils","generate energy faster.","§bRotor Efficiency","Rotor blades can only fully","capture energy from %d mB of","fluid per blade.","Efficiency drops if the flow","of input fluid rises past","capacity.","§bEnergy Storage","§bIntake Fluid Tank","§bExhaust Fluid Tank","Rotor Speed","Rotors perform best at","900 or 1800 RPM.","Rotors kept overspeed for too","long may fail.",
"Catastrophically.","§bFlow Rate Governor","Controls the maximum rate at","which hot fluids are drawn","from the turbine\'s intake tank","and passed over the turbines.","Effectively, the max rate at which","the turbine will process fluids.","§bIncrease Max Flow Rate","Higher flow rates will","increase rotor speed.","SHIFT: +10 mB","CTRL: +100mB","CTRL+SHIFT: +1000mB","§bDecrease Max Flow Rate","Lower flow rates will","decrease rotor speed.","SHIFT: -10 mB","CTRL: -100mB","CTRL+SHIFT: -1000mB","§bInduction Coils",
"Metal coils inside the turbine","extract energy from the rotor","and convert it into RF.","These controls engage/disengage","the coils.","§bEngage Coils","Engages the induction coils.","Energy will be extracted from","the rotor and converted to RF.","Energy extraction exerts drag","on the rotor, slowing it down.","§bDisengage Coils","Disengages the induction coils.","Energy will NOT be extracted from","the rotor, allowing it to","spin faster.","§bActivate Turbine","Enables flow of intake fluid to rotor.","Fluid flow will spin up the rotor.",
"§bDeactivate Turbine","Disables flow of intake fluid to rotor.","The rotor will spin down.","§bVent: All Exhaust","Dump all exhaust fluids.","The exhaust fluid tank","will not fill.","§bVent: Overflow Only","Dump excess exhaust fluids.","Excess fluids will be lost","if exhaust fluid tank is full.","§bVent: Closed","Preserve all exhaust fluids.","Turbine will slow or halt","fluid intake if exhaust","fluid tank is full.","Status: §4Inactive","Status: §2Active","%.1f RPM","%.0f RF/t","%d mB/t","%.1f%%","100%",
